        <Parent_String>bolts by form [300048622], bolts (fasteners) [300033325], bolts and bolt components [300246365], fasteners [300036363], components by general context [300241581], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
